Function SelectRange(sText As String, sTitle As String) As Range'Developed By Wojciech Dobrzycki, Last edit 25/10/2016'Function used to get range from selection, if it does not provide result it will give result = Nothing what may be later evaluated in code of macroDim rngHelp As RangeOn Error Resume Next    Set rngHelp = Application.InputBox(sText, sTitle, , , , , , 8)On Error GoTo 0Set SelectRange = rngHelpEnd Function
